President Bush, in a letter to Israeli Prime Minister Yitzhak Shamir, has 
echoed the statement of Secretary of State James A. Baker III that the idea of 
a "greater Israel" should be abandoned, National Public Radio said in a 
broadcast from Washington. Baker's exhortation, in a speech on May 22, was 
