<P>
9 ISRAELI JOURNALISTS VISITING SOVIET UNION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
JERUSALEM 
</P>
