<P>
INTERCHANGE CLOSINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Late-night bridge construction work will temporarily shut several portions of 
the Interstate 8-California 163 interchange this weekend, according to 
Caltrans. 
</P>
<P>
The following sections will be closed: east I-8 ramp to north California 163; 
south California 163 ramp to east I-8; Hotel Circle to east I-8 on-ramp, and 
the right-hand lane of I-8, from Hotel Circle to its junction with California 
163. 
</P>
<P>
The areas will close shortly before midnight Friday and reopen at 8 a.m. 
Saturday. The areas will again close at 9 p.m. Saturday and reopen at 8 a.m. 
Sunday. 
</P>
