STATES; OFFSHORE EXPLORATION; LEGISLATION -- UNITED STATES; OIL INDUSTRY -- 
UNITED STATES; LUJAN, MANUEL JR; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN INVESTMENTS; 
ENVIRONMENT 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
