NIBBLES AND BITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Austin G. Buffum, supervisor of music for the Capistrano Unified School 
District, has been given the Cyril Gallick Award, created in 1988 by the 
Capistrano Valley Symphony board of trustees to recognize local music 
educators. 
</P>
